    "—": {},
    "·": {
      "comment": "A period used to separate two related items.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true
    },
    "· Ended %@": {
      "comment": "A note that a session has ended.",
      "isCommentAutoGenerated": true
    },
    "“Not Here” (excused) is a soft mark — the student can still tap their card to sign in. “Absent” is a firm admin mark — only an admin can undo it.": {},
    "/": {},
    "%@": {},
